      • setFromString

        public def setFromString(sectionNumber : String,
                         level : int) : void 
        Description copied from class: SectionNumber
        Change this version number from the given string representation.

        The string representation should be integer numbers, separated by dot characters.

        Parameters:
        sectionNumber - the string representation of the version number.
        level - is the level at which the section number is visible (1 for the top level, 2 for subsections...)

      • toString

        public def toString(format : String) : String 
        Description copied from class: SectionNumber
        Format the section numbers.
        Parameters:
        format - the format. It must be compatible with MessageFormat, with the first parameter {0} equals to the first part of the full section number, and the second parameter {1} equals to a single section number.
        Returns:
        the formatted section number.
